info.title: Validated Healthcare Directory Server Capability Statement
info.description: This Capability Statement defines the expected capabilities of a validated healthcare directory FHIR server conforming to the Validated Healthcare Directory Implementation Guide.

contact.name: HL7 International - Patient Administration Work Group

parameters.name: accessibility
parameters.description: Select locations that offer the specified accessibility options

parameters.description: Select Locations with an identifier issued by the specified organization

parameters.description: Select Locations with the specified identifier

parameters.name: new-patient-network
parameters.description: Select locations that are part of the specified network and are/are not accepting new patients

parameters.name: new-patient
parameters.description: Select locations that are/are not accepting new patients

parameters.name: organization
parameters.description: Select Locations managed by the specified organization

parameters.name: partof
parameters.description: Select Locations that are part of the specified location

parameters.name: contains
parameters.description: Select locations that contain the specified co-ordinates

parameters.name: near
parameters.description:
Search for locations where the location.position is near to, or within a specified distance of, the provided coordinates expressed as [latitude]|[longitude]|[distance]|[units] (using the WGS84 datum, see notes).
If the units are omitted, then kms should be assumed. If the distance is omitted, then the server can use its own discretion as to what distances should be considered near (and units are irrelevant)

Servers may search using various techniques that might have differing accuracies, depending on implementation efficiency.

Requires the near-distance parameter to be provided also

parameters.description: Select Locations with the specified status
